o be employed to sparsify the network graph or reduce\nthe number of local exchanges between nodes, which saves sensors power in the\nwireless sensor networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Nov 2020 01:32:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-24"}
