ieces of conclusions on how to use GNNs and DE properly\nin tasks of node classification.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 22 Nov 2020 22:04:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Nov 2020 05:31:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 29 Nov 2020 19:31:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-01"}
